Backfill strategy to automatically backfill the Stream's
objects. Specific objects can be excluded.

This message has `oneof`_ fields (mutually exclusive fields).
For each oneof, at most one member field can be set at the same time.
Setting any member of the oneof automatically clears all other
members.

.. _oneof: https://proto-plus-python.readthedocs.io/en/stable/fields.html#oneofs-mutually-exclusive-fields

Attributes:

        backfilling.

        This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``excluded_objects``.
    mysql_excluded_objects (google.cloud.datastream_v1alpha1.types.MysqlRdbms):
        MySQL data source objects to avoid
        backfilling.

oracle_excluded_objects.description: Oracle data source objects to avoid backfilling.  This field is a member of `oneof`_ ``excluded_objects``.
